name: MyLastminutes
author: MarcoDuindam

sections.description:
So you want to use our plugin on your WordPress website? We have you covered! Mylastminutes gives you al the last minutes you want on your website.
Create a free account and start creating your desired top 10 last minute lists with your . Put it with a simple shortcode on your WordPress pages, widgets or posts.

sections.faq:
Is MyLastminutes free?

MyLastminutes is free to use.

Do you offer support for free users?

Yes. No matter if you’re free or premium user, we are here for you 24/7. Expect a 1h average response time and a 65% answer resolution in the first reply.

Got more questions? Contact us!
